wwutil.model.annotation
Annotation Type Key

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Key

Mark a field in a model class as the primary key of the class. There are two types of primary key: single Id or composite key with hashKey ane rangeKey. For Id primary key, a model class can only have one field declared as the Id field.
